title: [LAkiba] Kouryu Densetsu Villgust OVA 1 & 2 English Subs
description:
This is an anime comedy I&#039;ve been trying to track down for years. I finally found it so I&#039;m uploading it here.

Armed Dragon Fantasy Villgust is a parody of sorts based on two console RPGs by the same name. Eight chosen warriors are destined to stop a revived dark god and just about every other rpg cliche in the book, including but not limited to disintegrating monsters.
